item.description:
The New England Metaphysical Club is a discussion and social group focusing on the exploration of Metaphysical subjects.
Metaphysics has become a general term which can be defined as "outside of traditional science" and can involve everything from Philosophy to New Age subjects.
Members are encouraged to share their interests and beliefs, and to help choose topics for group focus!
Possible topics might include: Ancient religion and spirituality, UFO's, paranormal research, divination, philosophy, New Age, Law of Attraction, meditation, psychic phenomenon, magick, and of course much more.
Let's get to know each other and explore some fascinating subjects!

topics_item.name: Learn about the Law of Attraction & your vibration
